title: Buying Brands with Bobby Newman
itunes:title: Buying Brands with Bobby Newman
description: Bobby Newman from J.C. Newman joins the Cigar Authority to talk about  their new Mighty Mighty Maduro. We also smoke blind... 12 cigars we may  or may not have ever smoked. Can we (and you) guess them correctly? It's  time for The Cigar AUTHORITY!
